title: Chałupki, Busko County
text:
Chałupki is a <a href="village">village</a> in the administrative district of <a href="Gmina%20Tucz%C4%99py">Gmina Tuczępy</a>, within <a href="Busko%20County">Busko County</a>, <a href="%C5%9Awi%C4%99tokrzyskie%20Voivodeship">Świętokrzyskie Voivodeship</a>, in south-central Poland. It lies approximately west of <a href="Tucz%C4%99py%2C%20%C5%9Awi%C4%99tokrzyskie%20Voivodeship">Tuczępy</a>, north-east of <a href="Busko-Zdr%C3%B3j">Busko-Zdrój</a>, and south-east of the regional capital <a href="Kielce">Kielce</a>.
The village has a population of 230.
